<h1>Providore Fine Foods</h1>

<h4>Providore Fine Foods is a modern marketplace with European flair and Oregon roots.</h4>

<p>Located in Northeast Portland, Providore Fine Foods is a neighborhood fixture for daily customers and a dining and shopping destination for locals and visitors alike. You can visit us for elevated prepared foods and gourmet groceries, or spend an afternoon dining and enjoying a glass of beer or wine.</p>

<p>Anchor tenant Pastaworks and their Mediterranean rotisserie Arrosto, are joined by Flying Fish Co. + Oyster Bar, The Meat Monger, Rubinette Produce Market, Little T Baker, and Hilary Horvath Flowers to create an eating and grocery experience without parallel.</p>

